findings.title: Owner can change the tax, marketing and liquidity fee
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify the tax, marketing, and liquidity fees.

findings.title: Owner can change the maximum transaction amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the maximum transaction amount, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can exclude from the fee
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to exclude certain addresses or users from paying fees.

findings.title: Owner can change marketing wallet
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the marketing wallet.

findings.title: Owner can change number of tokens to add to liquidity
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify the number of tokens added to liquidity, which could lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw contract ETHs
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the privilege to withdraw contract ETHs.

findings.title: Owner can lock and unlock
findings.description: The owner has privileges to lock and unlock, allowing them to retake ownership even after renouncing it.
